SUMMARY:Lec56|ODEgen: Analytic Gradients of Quantum Pulse Programs|Korbinian Kottmann-Xanadu
LOCATION:https://tinyurl.com/gucs-zoom
DESCRIPTION:We introduce ODEgen\, a new method for evaluating analytic gradients of quantum pulse programs and contrast it with the stochastic parameter-shift rule. You will see numerics highlighting the advantages of ODEgen\, discussion of the required quantum resources and see code snippets on how to easily use these methods in PennyLane.
URL:https://qucs.info/lectures/56-odegen-analytic-gradients-of-quantum-pulse-programs
